WEBVTT

00:02:28.693 --> 00:02:31.879
where people perfect their craft
over generations.

00:02:31.903 --> 00:02:34.910
It's a culture that masters
both time and space,

00:02:34.934 --> 00:02:37.826
so that artists can truly
create with freedom.

00:02:38.282 --> 00:02:41.813
And what I discovered
was a place I wasn't angry with.

00:02:42.155 --> 00:02:44.369
Tokyo hadn't wronged me in any way.

00:02:44.393 --> 00:02:46.903
I could no longer create with anger

00:02:46.927 --> 00:02:48.465
or out of pain.

00:02:48.489 --> 00:02:52.253
I had to bravely allow myself
to create from a different place.

00:02:52.812 --> 00:02:55.693
And what I found is this incredible tool

00:02:55.717 --> 00:02:58.672
transcended a line on paper.

00:02:58.696 --> 00:03:00.070
I found this thing